document.title: Open Dutch Wordnet
document.intro: Open Dutch WordNet is a Dutch lexical semantic database. Open Dutch Wordnet contains 117914 synsets, of which the majority are nouns synsets: 98049. There are 18782 verb synsets and 1083 adjectival synsets. 51588 synsets contain at least one Dutch synonym, which leaves 66326 synsets sti...
